[05/23 04:08:44     14s] 	Write out the usage and options with brief descriptions.
[05/23 04:08:44     14s] [-lic_multi_cpu <lic_list>]
[05/23 04:08:44     14s] 	Control which licenses to use for higher multi-cpu usage in priority
[05/23 04:08:44     14s] 	order from left to right. The allowed license names are:
