[05/23 04:08:44     14s] 	"tpsxl tpsl vdst"
[05/23 04:08:44     14s] [-lic_startup_options <lic_list>]
[05/23 04:08:44     14s] 	Additional option licenses needed at startup. The allowed license
[05/23 04:08:44     14s] 	names are:
